這場枪击案的時間发生在奥兰多当地时间6月12日凌晨两点，凶嫌奥马尔·马丁在犯案前打电话给[[緊急救助電話|911]]，宣布自己效忠于伊斯兰国领袖[[阿布·贝克尔·巴格达迪|阿布·贝克尔·巴格达迪]]，然后持[[SIG_MCX突擊步槍|SIG MCX突擊步槍]]、[[格洛克17|格洛克17]]和疑似爆炸物品进入名为“脉冲”的同性恋酒吧开枪行凶，[[奥兰多警局|奥兰多警局]]的警察赶到与凶手交火。凶手退入酒吧并劫持人质。凌晨5点，防爆突击队强攻进入酒吧，与凶手交火，凶手被击毙，三十多名人质逃生。整个事件已经造成50人死亡，53人受伤。有幸存者称凶手在开枪过程中高呼“[[大赞辞|真主至大]]”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/pulse-nightclub-shooting-orlando/|title=Islamic terrorism tie eyed in Orlando gay bar shooting|publisher=|accessdate=2016-06-12|archive-date=2019-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190407203342/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/pulse-nightclub-shooting-orlando/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/multiple-injuries-shooting-orlando-nightclub-police/story?id=39789552|title=FL Club Shooting a 'Domestic Terror Incident,' Approx 20 Dead|first=A. B. C.|last=News|date=2016-06-12|publisher=|accessdate=2016-06-12|archive-date=2019-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190517023642/https://abcnews.go.com/US/multiple-injuries-shooting-orlando-nightclub-police/story?id=39789552|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="#1"/>

==犯罪嫌疑人==
枪击案凶手为29岁的美国公民[[奥马尔·马丁|奥马尔·马丁]]，是一名[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]，出生于[[纽约|纽约]]，其父母为[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]移民，其父親的口語是帶有[[普什圖|普什圖]]口音的[[達里語|達里語]]<ref name=dm3637414>{{Cite news |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3637414/Everyone-running-Gunman-bursts-gay-nightclub-Florida-shoots-20-people-taking-hostages.html |title=Orlando shooting at Pulse is worst mass shooting in history with at least 50 dead |work=Daily Mail Online |date=2016-06-12 |accessdate=2016-06-12 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308052953/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3637414/Everyone-running-Gunman-bursts-gay-nightclub-Florida-shoots-20-people-taking-hostages.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。警方怀疑枪手与伊斯兰极端宗教组织有关联，凶手过去也曾自称和“恐怖组织”有联系。<ref>{{cite news|title=Mass shooting at Pulse nightclub in Orlando, Florida|accessdate= |work=The Australian|date=2016-06-12|quote=The FBI has described the shooting as -{‘an act of terrorism’’}- and say they suspect the shooter had ties to radical Islam.}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://dailycaller.com/2016/06/12/fbi-suspect-bragged-about-ties-to-terrorist-organizations/|script-title=en:FBI: Suspect Bragged About Ties To ‘Terrorist Organizations’|last=|first=|date=2016-06-12|publisher=The Daily Caller|accessdate=2016-06-12|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308020009/https://dailycaller.com/2016/06/12/fbi-suspect-bragged-about-ties-to-terrorist-organizations/|dead-url=no}}</ref>《商业内幕》（Business Insider）报道称该恐怖袭击为“独狼式恐怖袭击”，没有证据显示奥马尔曾经直接受过IS组织的领导和训练，而是响应了IS“在各国就地发动圣战处决[[卡菲勒|卡菲勒]]”的号召。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/isis-statement-orlando-shooting-attack-2016-6/|title=Islamic terrorism tie eyed in Orlando gay bar shooting|publisher=|accessdate=2016-06-12|archive-date=2018-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180824112931/https://www.businessinsider.com/isis-statement-orlando-shooting-attack-2016-6|dead-url=no}}</ref>

奧馬爾的父親在接受媒體採訪時称兒子行凶的动机并非出于伊斯兰信仰，而是於數月前在[[邁阿密|邁阿密]]看到兩名男子在自己妻兒面前接吻後，感到非常憤怒。<ref name=dm3637414/>

奧馬爾本人疑為一名[[同性戀者|同性戀者]]，舊同學指曾邀請他一同到同性戀夜店。在事發夜店的一名表演者表示，他在3年前曾光顧過該夜店，並與另一男子跳舞。他還曾通过常见的同性戀交友[[應用程式|應用程式]]和[[同性戀者|同性戀者]]結交。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/national/former-classmates-recall-orlando-shooters-bizarre-reaction-on-911/2016/06/13/f08b2950-3187-11e6-95c0-2a6873031302_story.html|publisher=[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]|date=2016-06-13|title=Orlando gunman had been seen on gay dating apps, at Pulse nightclub before shooting|accessdate=2016-06-14|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809013523/https://www.washingtonpost.com/national/former-classmates-recall-orlando-shooters-bizarre-reaction-on-911/2016/06/13/f08b2950-3187-11e6-95c0-2a6873031302_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|publisher=[[每日郵報|每日郵報]]|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3639961/Orlando-terrorist-went-gay-club-Pulse-dozen-times-got-drunk-belligerent-talked-wife-kid-massacring-49-people-there.html|title=Omar Mateen was gay, says ex-wife and former friend: Orlando terrorist used homosexual dating app and visited Pulse at least a dozen times|date=2016-06-13|accessdate=2016-06-14|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224185426/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3639961/Orlando-terrorist-went-gay-club-Pulse-dozen-times-got-drunk-belligerent-talked-wife-kid-massacring-49-people-there.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==受害者==
枪案共造成包括枪手在内至少50人死亡，53人受伤（包括52位平民和1名警官），多名伤者伤势严重，在当地医院接受手术。<ref>{{cite web | first1=Krishnadev | last1=Calamur | first2=Matt | last2=Ford | url=http://www.theatlantic.com/news/archive/2016/06/orlando-nightclub-shooting/486713/ | title=Orlando Nightclub Attack: What We Know | publisher=[[The_Atlantic|The Atlantic]] | date=2016-06-12 | accessdate=2016-06-12 | archive-date=2016-06-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160612151926/http://www.theatlantic.com/news/archive/2016/06/orlando-nightclub-shooting/486713/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>事发的夜店距离奥兰多地区医疗中心仅仅三个街区的距离，大部分伤员均被送往該医院。<ref name="NYTInitial">{{cite news |title = Shooting at Orlando Nightclub Kills 50, Police Say |first = Lizette |last = Alvarez |first2 = Steve |last2 = Kenny |first3 = Richard |last3 = Pérez-Peña |authorlink3 = Richard Pérez-Peña |url = http://www.nytimes.com/2016/06/13/us/orlando-nightclub-shooting.html |accessdate = 2016-06-12 |newspaper = New York Times |date = 2016-06-12 |archive-date = 2016-06-12 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160612102027/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/06/13/us/orlando-nightclub-shooting.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>

奥兰多市政府在其官方网站上建立了受害者名单，公布已通知家属的受害者身份。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cityoforlando.net/blog/victims/|title=Victims|accessdate=2016-06-12|work=City of Orlando|archive-date=2016-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160612201808/http://www.cityoforlando.net/blog/victims/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

