s://www.whitehouse.gov/the-press-office/2016/06/12/presidential-proclamation-honoring-victims-attack-orlando-florida|work=WhiteHouse.gov|date=2016-06-12|accessdate=2016-06-12|archive-date=2016-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160613072642/https://www.whitehouse.gov/the-press-office/2016/06/12/presidential-proclamation-honoring-victims-attack-orlando-florida|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

